ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v26.datatype

Class LA1

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractType
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractComposite
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v26.datatype.LA1
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Composite, Type, Visitable, Serializable

    public class LA1
extends AbstractComposite

    Represents an HL7 LA1 (Location with Address Variation 1) data type. This type consists of the following components:

    • Point of Care (IS)
    • Room (IS)
    • Bed (IS)
    • Facility (HD)
    • Location Status (IS)
    • Patient Location Type (IS)
    • Building (IS)
    • Floor (IS)
    • Address (AD)
    See Also:
